<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cookpad Indonesia</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            color:black;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
       .jumbotron {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
       .card {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: #fff;
        }
       .card-img-top {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
       .card-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
       .card-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
       .card-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
       .btn-primary {
            background-color: #F4C524;
            border-color: #F4C524;
        }
       .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0069d9;
            border-color: #0062cc;
        }
       .logo {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="my-4"><img src="logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">Resep Kuy</h1>
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <p>Temukan dan bagikan resep - resep favoritmu dengan komunitas kami.</p>
            <form class="my-4">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" id="search-input" class="form-control" placeholder="Cari resep...">
                    <button type="submit" id="search-button" class="btn btn-primary">Cari</button>
                </div>
            </form>
            <p>Atau, <a href="#">periksa kategori kami</a> untuk mendapatkan inspirasi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <% recipes.forEach(recipe => { %>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="<%= recipe.image_recipe %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><%= recipe.title_recipe %></h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%= recipe.description_recipe %></p>
                        <a href="/recipes/<%= recipe.id_recipe %>" class="btn btn-primary">Lihat</a>
                    </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </div>

<script src="../controllers/search.js"></script>
</body>
</html>